snippet.title: Project Genesis: Minerva Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this video, we're showing off the latest pre-alpha milestone update for Project Genesis - Minerva, which features space combat and FPS gameplay!

Make sure to check out our website and social media pages for more information on Project Genesis, as well as our pre-alpha Minerva milestone update!

Wishlist us on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/700240/Project_Genesis/

Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/6pHSb4P

Follow us on the socials:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/8circuitstudios & https://twitter.com/play_projectgenesis
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/8circuitstudios
